dataset.title: ParcelsRealEstate
dataset.description:
Notice:

1. If you download this feature layer on our "Open data" website. The process may be slow. This feature layer is very large. 

2. Several field names are truncated or altered when you download the data. The field names (within the download) will not match the attribute field names listed below in this description.

 

This feature layer contains the most current parcels data with real estate data for DuPage County, Illinois. The dataset was created and is maintained by the DuPage County Information Technology Department, GIS Division in conjunction with the DuPage County Clerk for the visual and spatial representation of deeds, road rights-of-way, and subdivision plats. The ParcelsRealEstate feature layer contains the Current Assessment Parcels as well as the Current Real Estate File which is joined to the parcels on a weekly basis.

 

DuPage County Parcel Data: NOTE: Field ACRE_SOURCE = 0 is Calculated, 1 is Deeded, NULL is unverified.

 

FIELDS IN ParcelsRealEstateCC:

OBJECTID Long Integer 4 General Info: Object Identification Number.

 

PIN Text 10 General Info: Parcel Identification Number.

ACREAGE  Long Integer General Info: Acreage of a Parcel. 

ACRE_SOURCE Long Integer General Info: Acre Source values = 0 is Calculated, 1 is Deeded, NULL is unverified.

BILLNAME Text 25 General Info: Billing Name.

BILLSTNUM Text 6 General Info: Billing Street Number.

BILLSTDIR Text 1 General Info: Billing Street Direction.

BILLSTNAME Text 16 General Info: Billing Street Name.

BILLAPT Text 6 General Info: Billing Apartment.

BILLCITY Text 18 General Info: Billing City.

BILLSTATE Text 2 General Info: Billing State.

BILLZIP Text 5 General Info: Billing ZIPCODE.

BILLZIPSUF Text 4 General Info: Billing ZIP Suffix.

PROPNAME Text 25 General Info: Property Name.

PROPSTNUM Text 6 General Info: Property Street Number.

PROPSTDIR Text 1 General Info: Property Street Direction.

PROPSTNAME Text 16 General Info: Property Street Name.

PROPAPT Text 6 General Info: Property Apartment.

PROPCITY Text 18 General Info: Property City.

PROPSTATE Text 2 General Info: Property State.

PROPZIP Text 5 General Info: Property ZIPCODE.

PROPZIPSUF Text 4 General Info: Property ZIPCODE Suffix.

PARCELSTAT Text 3 General Info: Parcel Status.

EXEMPTCODE Text 1 General Info: Parcel Exempt Code.

PROPCLASS Text 1 General Info: Property Classification.

 Values:

   F = Farm

   H = Farm_Homesite

   C = Commercial

   I = Industrial

   A = Apartment

   R = Residential

   M = Prop_Multiple

BILLVALUE Long Integer 4 General Info: Billing Value.
